Karitane
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number: 2
Definition:Describing or pertaining to Karitane nurses or nursing, or the Plunket Society, from the noun, and its further use for the nursing headquarters of the Plunket Society: hence used in many gen. and special combinations: - foods, put out by the Society ("Karitane' is the brand-name for Plunket Society products), - nurse,-hospital.


